longDescription: This core supporter pack includes 4,800 Points total, the Orion Supporter Forum Title, Orion Armour Pack, Orion Hood, Orion Back Attachment, Orion Apparition Effect, Orion Portal Effect, Orion Weapon Effect, Orion Portrait Frame, Path of Exile Signed Art Pack and everything in the Judicator Supporter Pack.
